        <odd id="ref9">
            <head>Early American History Note</head>
            <p>This collection consists of letters from William Spencer to Caroline Watts about a range of topics, most of which relate to affairs in England during the nineteenth century. He discusses current affairs, like the Corn laws, and scientific and pedagogical issues.</p>
        </odd>
